        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股全日跌462點 內房逆市升  科指一周跌逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股全日挫462點，曾跌505點破上午低位，失20天線，藥業股午後跌幅擴大，晶片股、電動車及相關股、金屬股俱挫，內房股午後升。一周計恒指及國指俱趺逾3%，科指跌逾半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收跌462點或1.73%，報26290點，午後跌破上午低位，見26247，跌505點或1.89%，今早開跌228點或0.85%，報26523點，上午中段見26558點，跌幅收窄至194點或0.73%，為全日高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_03939-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_03939-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_03939-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日跌211點或3.27%，報6259點，今早開跌90點或1.4%，報6380點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日跌171點或1.8%，報9358點，今早開跌89點或 0.94%，報9440點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指跌484點或1.81%，報26282，低水8點 ; 科指期貨全日報6251，跌232點或3.58%，低水9點 ; 國指期貨報9349，跌184點或1.93%，低水9點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交3337.37億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">午後A股跌幅擴大，港股跌勢加劇。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周累計，恒生指數跌850點或3.13% ; 恒生科技指數跌363點或5.45% ; 恒生國企指數跌308點或3.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥業股午後瀉，藥明生物(02269)收瀉7.57%，報37.76元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 藥明康德(02359)跌5.87%，報112.4元 ; 翰森製藥(03692)跌2.16%，報36.22元。藥明合聯(02268)挫7.29%，報71.85元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股挫，中芯國際(00981)跌7.13%，報77.55元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位，推低恒指42點 ; 華虹半導體(01347)跌4.05%，報81.75元 ; 上海復旦(01385)跌5.98%，報42.44元。內地傳媒報道，多家券商把多隻A股晶片股融資融券折算率統一調整為零，包括中芯國際、華虹公司等，A股晶片股也顯著回落。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">黃金及基本金屬股齊挫。萬國黃金(03939)全日瀉11.81%，報35.7元 ; 紫金(02899)跌6.86%，報33.66元; 紫金黃金國際(02259)挫7.71%，報130.4元 ; 招金(01818)跌7.43%，報32.14元 ; 江西銅業(00358)也報36.42元，跌4.36% ; 中國宏橋(01378)跌5.98%，報26.1元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_03939-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_03939-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：萬國黃金2024年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍頭科網股拖低大市，阿里巴巴(09988)跌4.56%，報165.4元 ; 騰訊(00700)跌3.55%，報651.6元，兩股拖低恒指200點。百度(09888)跌5.69%，報125.9元 ; 快手(01024)跌5.52%，報83.9元。   </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電池股沽壓大，寧德時代(03750)全日瀉7.18%，報543元 ; 贛鋒鋰業(01772)大插10.75%，報45.56元 ; 天齊鋰業(09696)挫9.92%，報43.78元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電動車股也受壓，小鵬(09868)跌4.18%，報87.05元 ; 理想汽車(02015)跌2.59%，報92.15元 ; 蔚來(09866)跌5.09%，報57.8元; 比亞迪(01211)跌1.82%，報108.2元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內房股午後升，央視報導，武漢國慶及中秋假期一手及二手樓成交量俱升，中海外(00688)升2.46%，報14.16元 ; 恒隆地產(00101)升2.05%，報8.98元; 華潤置地(01109)升1.17%，報29.46元 ; 華潤萬象(01209)升1.82%，報40.3元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15333278-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c462%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%a7%e6%88%bf%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%87-%e7%a7%91%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c",
