            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市高位回吐。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數收報48088點，跌491點，跌幅1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，日股升5%</p>\n</div>",
